Italy Regulator to Examine Parmalat Bid ‘Rapidly,’ Stampa Says

-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 
2011-05-01T09:28:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-01/italy-regulator-to-examine-parmalat-bid-rapidly-stampa-says.html
Consob, Italy’s financial-markets
watchdog, will examine Groupe Lactalis’s bid for  Parmalat SpA (PLT) 
“rapidly,” Giuseppe Vegas, the chairman of the regulator, said
in an interview with  La Stampa   “The purposes of the offer should be clear,” Vegas was
quoted as saying by the Turin-based newspaper. Consob also wants
more information from Lactalis about the financing of the bid,
he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tommaso Ebhardt in Milan at 
 tebhardt@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chad Thomas at   cthomas16@bloomberg.net . 